{"tid":1565753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微博係一個令人大開眼界既地方 厲害了我的國！","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T15:19:52.000Z","uid":228441,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aca299357d50734d194c46da98d7055eabd746ec","tid":1565753,"uid":228441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"唔可以唔讚既地方係，支共既洗腦式教育非常成功，稍係有理智既人少型有少，例子如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhpeNtY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhpeNtY.png&h=a44b69b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有隻支那整容雞去反港獨，去任地神社埋香港人既牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最好笑既係條友仔用緊iphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEySy98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEySy98.png&h=fd1b3273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有香港人外國人上去鬧佢，跟住就忍唔住要吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。其實大家唔使睇，都知道係咩中國係你呀爸個d論調<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但最估唔到既係，竟然有清醒既中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cRUiuKv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcRUiuKv.png&h=18905abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個仲抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CiRg0RD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCiRg0RD.png&h=acb2dead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇，咦原來黑警都有微博,d白衫狗輪住黎接受訪問<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dQYuM2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dQYuM2.png&h=bf91bcb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇下有關香港既熱門,無一個係同今次運動既訴求有關，畀d鄉下仔睇到，難怪會明白佢地諗野點解會咁偏激<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/2KPVw0X.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KPVw0X.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=a1f3073a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/2KPVw0X.png[/img］</a><br />\n<br />\n所以見到班人既留言已經冇嬲既感覺，因為好理解佢地，清楚佢地點解咁撚無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Y7W0Vx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Y7W0Vx.png&h=4f1d48e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有，呢條光頭星真係丟晒香港人既架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de210e2f7114ec92b228333377f8fe046d91f808","tid":1565753,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f6c5c47ebe1311c1146cec1c4730b1a85858ed7d","tid":1565753,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:19:52.000Z","msg":"[突發 - 國際線] Humans of New York 黎香港!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566182</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比國際睇到前線手足經歷左咩"}]}